UNRELIABLE - net.marfgamer.jraknet.protocol.Reliability
The packet packet will be sent, but it is not guaranteed that it will be received.
UNRELIABLE_SEQUENCED - net.marfgamer.jraknet.protocol.Reliability
Same as UNRELIABLE, however it will not be handled if a newer sequenced packet on the channel has already arrived.
UNRELIABLE_WITH_ACK_RECEIPT - net.marfgamer.jraknet.protocol.Reliability
Same as UNRELIABLE, however you will be notified whether the packet was lost or received through onAcknowledge() and onNotAcknowledge() methods through the RakNetServerListener and RakNetClientListener classes.
